    public class Arrow
extends AbstractNode
implements IsDefaultsArrow, HasBorderOptions, HasShadowOptions, HasExtendedShadowOptions, HasBackgroundColor
    Implements a ARROWHEADS, and its start and end nodes, to apply on a LINE annotation.
